#home
  #not_yet
    #copy.trans
      %h1 Sorry, but Givey.org is invite only right now.
      
      %p
        Our crack psychologists are busy figuring out the best way 
        to gently probe the your psyche to find your most (and least) 
        altruistic friends. 
        
