        In the meantime, we invite you to follow us on Facebook and Twitter.  
        
      %p
        = link_to image_tag('icons/twitter_64.png'), 'http://www.twitter.com/giveyorg'
        = link_to image_tag('icons/facebook_64.png'), 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Giveyorg/121752667894755'
        
